{"tid":1969874,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連仔開個Memes台有無得諗？","createTime":"2020-04-12T17:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T02:19:49.000Z","uid":158996,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1a7c2f8dfc674ea1a5e762cd86534fc5186b7383","tid":1969874,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T17:27:40.000Z","msg":"今日連登比泰中大戰激發咗對memes嘅想像力同討論，要培養meme文化，由實踐開始最好<br />\n<br />\n運作模式同reddit類似，喺memes台入面可以開啲專門topic，例如：<br />\nCCTVB戰線<br />\n白粉報戰線<br />\n4點鐘狗會<br />\nYoutuber大戰<br />\n乜都好，memes用正負皮判斷，簡單直接<br />\n講求幽默感同賤咀，拋開道德觀念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又可以交換memes素材，<br />\n二次創作人哋嘅二次創作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係泰國網民memes精選：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/81TRfbO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F81TRfbO.jpg&h=56a0d232&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C1GbZDu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC1GbZDu.jpg&h=3732f8a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/diU81RQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdiU81RQ.jpg&h=3dc190b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mbM3QLa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmbM3QLa.jpg&h=6d4302fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GRLcJ5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGRLcJ5a.jpg&h=153cd34a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實一個ppt都已經改到圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba3bbb6b2e5ef7ba409cea1edcc8a37e0b3e592","tid":1969874,"uid":55162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T17:29:05.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n想學下整meme <br />\n但英文麻麻"},{"pid":"ccf04443474340cfdae25135fa6b1a4c83d52afb","tid":1969874,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislik